[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說佛母出生三法藏般若",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "波羅蜜多經卷第二十一",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝奉大夫試光祿卿",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "傳法大師賜紫臣施護奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "學品第二十五",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩欲學一切智，當云何學？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若盡學則學一切智，若離學則學一切智。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無生無滅無起無染無性，如虛空法界寂靜等學，則學一切智。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩盡學離學乃至法界寂靜等學，則學一切智者，是等當云何作？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝若如是說，是等云何作者。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，如來證如如故得名如來，是如有盡、有所作不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「不也，世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如無盡相亦無所作。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，如來證如如故得名如來，是如有生有滅有起有染有得有證不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「不也，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b29_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩學一切智亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658b29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩摩訶薩若如是學者不盡如相，如是學者是學一切智，如是學者是學般若波羅蜜多，如是學者是學佛地，如是學者是學佛十力、四無所畏等一切佛法乃至一切智智，如是學者能到諸學彼岸，如是學者普能降伏魔及魔眾，如是學者速得不退轉法，如是學者速坐道場，如是學者是學三轉十二行相法輪，如是學者學自所行，如是學者學為他作所依怙法，如是學者是學大慈大悲大喜大捨，如是學者學度眾生界，如是學者是學不斷佛種，如是學者學開甘露門。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此廣大學是最上學，凡夫下劣人不能如是學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有能調御一切眾生，欲與一切眾生為依怙者，欲出過一切眾生界者，彼能如是學。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是學者，不墮地獄、餓鬼、畜生等趣，不生阿修羅界，不生邊地，不生旃陀羅族，不生下姓種族，不生種種卑賤巧業等族。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c15_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者，不失一目不盲兩目，亦不角睞，不聾不啞，不傴僂，不攣躄。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c18_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不醜陋，不麁惡，不形殘，不異相，亦無疥癩癰疽乾痟等病，不壞諸根人相圓滿，音聲清巧眾所愛樂。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c19_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c22_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又菩薩摩訶薩如是學者，不害他命，不盜他物，不行邪染，不虛妄言亦不兩舌復不惡口，不無義語，不生貪著，不起瞋惱，不住邪見，不邪命活，不修邪命法，不畜破戒眷屬，不近非法者，不生長壽天，雖入諸禪而不隨禪生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c22_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c27_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩以能成就善巧方便故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c27_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而菩薩成就何等善巧方便？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c28_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所謂從般若波羅蜜多相應出生善巧方便，是故菩薩雖入諸禪而不隨禪生。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0658c28_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a01_28",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩能如是學者，即得清淨十力、清淨四無所畏乃至清淨一切佛法。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a01_29",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切法自性本來清淨，菩薩摩訶薩云何復得清淨十力、清淨四無所畏乃至清淨一切佛法耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告須菩提言：「如是，如是！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切法自性本來清淨，菩薩摩訶薩於是一切法自性本來清淨中，如理修學般若波羅蜜多，不驚不怖不退不沒。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼諸愚異生等於如是法不知不見，以不知不見故無所覺了。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a10_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩摩訶薩發勤精進於中修學，自所學已，令諸異生等於是法中如理修學、實知實見。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩由如是學故，即得清淨十力、清淨四無所畏乃至清淨一切佛法。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩如是學者，悉能了知一切眾生心心所行。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如大地少出閻浮檀金，多諸荊棘砂礫草木等類。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切眾生亦復如是，於眾生聚中少能愛樂修學般若波羅蜜多者，多有愛樂修學聲聞、緣覺法門。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如眾生聚中少有修彼輪王業者，但多修彼諸小王業。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知眾生聚中少有行於般若波羅蜜多道者，多有行於聲聞、緣覺道者，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如眾生聚中少有修彼帝釋福業，但多修彼諸天子業。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知眾生聚中少有修習般若波羅蜜多行者，多有修習聲聞、緣覺行者，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如眾生聚中少有修彼梵王福業，但多修彼諸梵眾業。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a27_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知眾生聚中少有不退轉於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，多有退轉於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是義故，當知眾生聚中少有能發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心者，於少能發心中又復少能如理修行者，於少能修行中又復少能修習般若波羅蜜多相應行者，於少能修習相應行中又復少能於阿耨多羅三藐三菩提住不退轉者。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故諸菩薩摩訶薩若欲在少中少者，應當修習般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩修學是般若波羅蜜多者，不生雜染心、不生疑惑心、不生憎嫉心、不生慳悋心、不生破戒心、不生瞋惱心、不生懈怠心、不生散亂心、不生愚癡心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩應修學是般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此般若波羅蜜多能護諸波羅蜜多、能受諸波羅蜜多、能取諸波羅蜜多、能集諸波羅蜜多、能攝諸波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如六十二見，身見中攝，諸波羅蜜多於般若波羅蜜多中攝，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如士夫所有諸根，皆悉於其命根中攝，一切善法皆於般若波羅蜜多中攝，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如士夫命根滅時諸根皆滅，菩薩摩訶薩亦復如是，若智慧滅時一切善法而亦隨滅。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩摩訶薩若欲護諸波羅蜜多，若欲攝諸波羅蜜多者，應當修學是般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，菩薩摩訶薩若欲於一切眾生中福德最勝為上首者，應當修學是般若波羅蜜多。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次，佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何，三千大千世界一切眾生是為多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "但此閻浮提中所有眾生尚多無數，何況三千大千世界一切眾生。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使如是三千大千世界一切眾生，一一修行皆住菩薩地，或有一人盡其壽命，以諸飲食、衣服、臥具、醫藥及餘樂具，供養如是三千大千世界諸菩薩眾。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此人以是因緣得福多不？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「甚多，世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "甚多，善逝！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若復有人於一彈指頃能修行是般若波羅蜜多者，其所得福倍勝於前。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多廣大利益諸菩薩摩訶薩，復能護助阿耨多羅三藐三菩提故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c12_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故諸菩薩摩訶薩若欲於一切眾生中最勝無上，若欲與一切眾生為所依怙，若欲偏入諸佛境界，若欲具足佛功德法，若欲得佛遊戲神通，若欲作佛大師子吼，若欲得佛諸所行處，若欲普以三千大千世界大會說法。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩若欲成就如是等功德利者，應學是般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "學是般若波羅蜜多，不能圓滿諸功德利者，無有是處。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩亦具足聲聞功德利耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩亦學是聲聞法，亦具足聲聞功德之利。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩雖如是學、如是知、得如是利，而不於中生住著心。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c23_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩亦說彼聲聞法，而不取是法。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c24_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c25_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩如是學者，能為一切世間天、人、阿修羅等作大福田，而菩薩所作福田最上最勝，過餘聲聞、緣覺所有福田。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c26_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c28_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者是行般若波羅蜜多，得近一切智，不捨般若波羅蜜多，不離般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0659c29_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是學者不退失一切智，遠離聲聞、緣覺心，得近阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩作是念：『此是般若波羅蜜多，此名般若波羅蜜多，學是般若波羅蜜多故當得一切智。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是分別者，不名修學般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩於般若波羅蜜多不生分別，無知無見亦無所得，以如是不分別、無知見、無所得故，是名修學般若波羅蜜多。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "幻喻品第二十六",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，帝釋天主即起是念：「若菩薩摩訶薩修學是般若波羅蜜多者，尚能勝過一切眾生，何況成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當知，若有人愛樂一切智者，彼人得大善利善自活命，何況能發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心者，當知是人為一切眾生共所敬愛，普能調御一切眾生。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主作是念已，即時化諸曼陀羅華，滿自掌中散於佛上。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "華散佛已，合掌向佛作如是言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心者，普願得成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，普願圓滿一切佛法，圓滿一切智相應之法，圓滿自然智法，圓滿無漏法，普願一切眾生度生死岸證涅槃道，攝眾生心普令圓滿。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a25_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我見生死中有種種苦，我不欲令初發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心者，於一念中有所退轉，又不欲令已得安住阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，於一念中或生退轉，是故我欲普令成就阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "能發心者，廣大利益悲愍一切世間天、人、阿修羅等。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660a29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自得度已，復於一切眾生起如是心，未解脫者普令解脫，未得度者普令得度，未涅槃者普令涅槃。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有善男子、善女人，於初發心菩薩所，以彼所有諸功德法生隨喜心，若於久修習菩薩所生隨喜心，若於住不退轉菩薩所生隨喜心，若於一生補處菩薩所生隨喜心，於如是等能生隨喜心善男子、善女人，當說何者得福德多？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告帝釋天主言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "妙高山王尚可稱量知其限數，彼善男子、善女人以是諸隨喜心所獲福德，不可稱量知其限數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如四大洲界亦可稱量知其限數，彼善男子、善女人以是諸隨喜心所獲福德，不可稱量知其限數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如小千世界亦可稱量知其限數，彼善男子、善女人，以是諸隨喜心所獲福德，不可稱量知其限數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b15_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如中千世界亦可稱量知其限數，彼善男子、善女人以是諸隨喜心所獲福德，不可稱量知其限數。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b18_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如三千大千世界亦可稱量知其限數，彼善男子、善女人以是諸隨喜心所獲福德，不可稱量知其限數。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有人不能於初發心菩薩所，乃至不能於一生補處菩薩所，生隨喜心者，當知是人惡魔所著、為魔眷屬，從彼魔天命終而來生此。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸隨喜心而能破壞諸惡魔故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復，若人能生諸隨喜心者，是人應以隨喜功德迴向阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，以是迴向故而能增長阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660b27_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故當知，能生如是諸隨喜心者，是人不離佛、不離法、不離僧，增長一切最勝功德。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告帝釋天主言：「如是，如是！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若有人能生如是諸隨喜心者，是人不離佛、不離法、不離僧，增長一切最勝功德。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又，憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人能生如是諸隨喜心者，當知是善男子、善女人速得值佛。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝釋天主白佛言：「如是，世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，善逝！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子、善女人能生如是諸隨喜心者，是善男子、善女人速得值佛。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復，以是隨喜善根力故，在在所生人所尊重恭敬讚歎。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人，眼根清淨不觀惡色，耳根清淨不聞惡聲，鼻根清淨不嗅惡香，舌根清淨不了惡味，身根清淨不染非觸。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c12_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復，不墮惡趣，生人、天道。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人成就無量無數隨喜善根故，常樂利樂一切眾生，以能生是隨喜心故，而能增長阿耨多羅三藐三菩提行，漸漸得成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人得菩提已，廣度無量無數眾生普令涅槃。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告帝釋天主言：「憍尸迦！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如汝所說，皆是如來威神護念。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人能生如是諸隨喜心者，是善男子、善女人深種善根，以是善根廣為無量無數眾生作大利益。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此因緣故，而能增長一切善法，漸漸得成阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，尊者須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心如幻故，云何以是心得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告尊者須菩提言：「於意云何，汝見有心如幻耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0660c29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「不也，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝見幻相可得耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「不也，世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我不見有心如幻，亦不見幻相可得。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝以是心是相可得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「不也，世尊！」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何，若不見有心如幻及幻相者，離是心是相，汝見有法可得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提言：「不也，世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "離如幻心及彼幻相，亦不見有法可得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a09_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若離如幻心及離幻相有法可見者，是法亦不可說是有是無，是故一切法畢竟離中，不可說有不可說無。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若一切法畢竟離故，阿耨多羅三藐三菩提亦畢竟離，般若波羅蜜多亦畢竟離。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以一切法畢竟離故，即無法可修亦無法可得，以一切法無所得故，阿耨多羅三藐三菩提亦不可得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以是畢竟離故菩薩摩訶薩亦畢竟離。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩摩訶薩因般若波羅蜜多故，得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而菩薩摩訶薩畢竟離，阿耨多羅三藐三菩提亦畢竟離。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a19_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者，云何以離得離耶？」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛讚須菩提言：「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a23_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切法畢竟離，般若波羅蜜多亦畢竟離，阿耨多羅三藐三菩提亦畢竟離，菩薩摩訶薩亦畢竟離。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而諸菩薩摩訶薩於是法中，如實了知般若波羅蜜多畢竟離故，即非般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a26_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故諸菩薩摩訶薩，雖因般若波羅蜜多故得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，而於是中無法可取、無法可得。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661a28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以無取無得故，菩薩摩訶薩雖得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，而非以離得離。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如我解佛所說義，此甚深義菩薩摩訶薩行者是為甚難。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此甚深義菩薩摩訶薩行者是為甚難。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b07_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩行此甚深義者，不於中道取證聲聞、緣覺之果，斯為甚難。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "須菩提白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如我解佛所說義，菩薩摩訶薩所為非難。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一切法無所得無所證。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以無得無證故，是中無證者、無所證、無所用證法，是故菩薩摩訶薩所為非難。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩聞作是說，不驚不怖不退不沒者，當知彼菩薩摩訶薩是為行般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖如是行，亦不見我行般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若如是不見所行般若波羅蜜多相故，是菩薩摩訶薩得近阿耨多羅三藐三菩提，即能遠離聲聞、緣覺之地，是行般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如虛空不作是念：『是遠是近？』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "虛空無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，不作是念：『阿耨多羅三藐三菩提去我近，聲聞、緣覺地去我遠。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如幻所化人不作是念：『彼幻師去我近，餘觀者去我遠。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "幻所化人無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，不作是念：『阿耨多羅三藐三菩提去我近，聲聞、緣覺地去我遠。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b25_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如諸影不作是念：『影所因者去我近，非所因者去我遠。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "影無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，不作是念：『阿耨多羅三藐三菩提去我近，聲聞、緣覺地去我遠。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661b29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如如來於一切眾生無憎無愛。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c04_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來一切憎愛斷故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c04_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，無憎無愛。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c04_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c05_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多非憎愛法。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c05_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如如來離諸分別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c06_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c06_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如來一切分別斷故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，離諸分別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如佛所化人不作是念：『阿耨多羅三藐三菩提去我近，聲聞、緣覺地去我遠。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c09_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "化人無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，不作是念：『阿耨多羅三藐三菩提去我近，聲聞、緣覺地去我遠。』",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如佛所化人隨所作事悉能成辦，雖所成辦而無分別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "化人無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，若一切法隨所修習悉能成辦。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多無分別故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又如工巧師，以其方便用機關木作男女相，隨所作事悉能成辦，雖所成辦而無分別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "巧幻所作故。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多亦復如是，若一切法隨所修習悉能成辦，雖有所成而無分別。",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "般若波羅蜜多無分別故。」",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說佛母出生三法藏般若波羅蜜多經卷第二十一",
        "from": "T08n0228_021:0661c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]